REFERENCE           18KYK001
LANG_ENGLISH        "Grife, it's good to get out of that rain.  Now we need to get up into the castle.  There's a turbolift over there."
LANG_CZECH        "Uff, jeste ze jsme pryc z toho deste. Ted se musime dostat do pevnosti. Tamhle je turbovytah."

REFERENCE           18KYK002
LANG_ENGLISH        "Hmmm... locked down.  Ever feel like you're not welcome?  Let's see if we can find another way out of here."
LANG_CZECH        "Hmmm... zamceno.  Nezda se ti, ze tu nejsme vitani?  Zkusime najit jinou cestu pryc."

REFERENCE           18KYK003
NOTES               "(shaking his head)"
LANG_ENGLISH        "They always lock the door... you think they'd have learned by now."
LANG_CZECH        "Vzdycky zamykaji dvere... jeden by si myslel, ze uz se to naucili."

REFERENCE           18KYK004
NOTES               "(checking the door)"
LANG_ENGLISH        "Doesn't look like there's a key.  That would be too easy."
LANG_CZECH        "Nevypada to, ze potrebuji klic.  To by bylo moc jednoduche."

REFERENCE           18KYK005
NOTES               "(sighs in frustration)"
LANG_ENGLISH        "The console to unlock the door's probably hidden in some room twelve floors up or something.  How does that make sense?"
LANG_CZECH        "Konzole na odemykani dveri je nejspis ukryta v nejake mistnosti o dvanact pater vis. To nedava smysl!"

REFERENCE           18KYK006
LANG_ENGLISH        "Wonder where this leads..."
LANG_CZECH        "Zajimalo by me, kam tohle vede..."

REFERENCE           18KYK007
LANG_ENGLISH        "Ugh... of course, it has to be a garbage pit, doesn't it?  Well, let's go, no one ever said being a Jedi was glamorous."
LANG_CZECH        "Uff... samozrejme, to musi byt odpadni sachta, ze ano?  Hm, pojdme. Nikdo netvrdil, ze byt Jediem je atraktivni."

REFERENCE           18KYK008
LANG_ENGLISH        "Jaden!  Run to the middle!  You can jump out there!"
LANG_CZECH        "Jadene!  Bez k prostredku!  Muzes odtamtud skocit!"

REFERENCE           18KYK009
LANG_ENGLISH        "That was too close.  We've gotta get outta here.  Take that chute and I'll take this one.  With luck, we'll meet up on the other side. "
LANG_CZECH        "To bylo tesne.  Musime se odsud dostat.  Jdi tamtou cestou, ja pujdu touhle. S trochou stesti se setkame na druhe strane. "

REFERENCE           18KYK010
LANG_ENGLISH        "Well, that worked out well. I thought I'd have to search high and low for you."
LANG_CZECH        "No, vyslo to. Myslel jsem, ze te budu muset hledat."

REFERENCE           18KYK011
LANG_ENGLISH        "This lift is locked down, too."
LANG_CZECH        "Tenhle vytah je take zamceny."

REFERENCE           18KYK012
LANG_ENGLISH        "Maybe this switch..."
LANG_CZECH        "Mozna tenhle prepinac..."

REFERENCE           18KYK013
NOTES               "(annoyed that it didn't work)"
LANG_ENGLISH        "Oh, come on..."
LANG_CZECH        "Ale, no tak..."

REFERENCE           18KYK014
NOTES               "(reacting to a console that starts beeping)"
LANG_ENGLISH        "Uh-oh."
LANG_CZECH        "Ale ne."

REFERENCE           18KYK015
LANG_ENGLISH        "Jaden, watch out!!!"
LANG_CZECH        "Jadene, pozor!!!"

REFERENCE           18KYK016
NOTES               "(straining)"
LANG_ENGLISH        "Uhh... Jaden... Find a way to drain the water!  If this power conduit... hits the floor... we're both gonna be fried!"
LANG_CZECH        "Ee... Jadene... najdi zpusob jak odcerpat vodu!  Jestli se to vedeni... dotkne podlahy... oba nas to upece!"

REFERENCE           18KYK017
LANG_ENGLISH        "Well look at that.  Guess we made our own path."
LANG_CZECH        "No vida.  Udelali jsme si vlastni cestu."

REFERENCE           18JAK001
LANG_ENGLISH        "Kyle!"
LANG_CZECH        "#same"

REFERENCE           18KYK018
