LANG_ENGLISH        "Relax, kid, I've seen tubes like this before; we can ride them to the top!"
LANG_CZECH        "Klid, chlapce, uz jsem takove trubky videl; muzeme se svezt nahoru!"

REFERENCE           18KYK019
NOTES               "(yelling over the wind)"
LANG_ENGLISH        "If we hit that laser grid, we're done for!  Head for that grate!"
LANG_CZECH        "Jestli se dotkneme toho laseroveho pole, mame po srande!  Na ten vycnelek!"

REFERENCE           18KYK020
NOTES               "(sarcastically)"
LANG_ENGLISH        "Well, that was fun."
LANG_CZECH        "No, byla to zabava."

REFERENCE           18KYK021
LANG_ENGLISH        "Not again.  Why even put doors in this place if they're always gonna be locked?!"
LANG_CZECH        "Uz zase.  Proc sem davaji dvere, kdyz musi byt porad zamcene?!"

REFERENCE           18KYK022
NOTES               "(seeing the dangerous tunnel)"
LANG_ENGLISH        "You gotta be kidding me."
LANG_CZECH        "To si delate srandu."

REFERENCE           18KYK023
NOTES               "(sarcastically)"
LANG_ENGLISH        "Remind me to have a talk with the architect when we're done here."
LANG_CZECH        "Pripomen mi, ze az tu skoncime, musim si promluvit s architektem."

REFERENCE           18KYK032
