LANG_CZECH        "Konecne!  Vytah, ktery funguje."

REFERENCE           18KYK025
LANG_ENGLISH        "The castle's still a few more levels up, but they've shut down the lifts above us.  Looks like we gotta find another way up."
LANG_CZECH        "Pevnost je porad o par pater vys, ale vypnuli vsechny vytahy. Budeme muset najit jinou cestu."

REFERENCE           18KYK026
LANG_ENGLISH        "Maybe we can move those mirrors to feed the energy back into the machine and overload it."
LANG_CZECH        "Mozna bychom mohli hnout temi zrcadly a odrazit energii zpatky. Mozna se pretizi."

REFERENCE           18KYK027
LANG_ENGLISH        "Good idea!  We can feed the energy back into the machine and overload it!"
LANG_CZECH        "Dobry napad!  Obratime energii zpatky a pretizime ten stroj!"

