LANG_CZECH        "Jadene, jsi v poradku?"

REFERENCE           18JAK003
LANG_ENGLISH        "Yeah, I'm fine, where are you?"
LANG_CZECH        "Jo, jsem v poradku, kde jste?"

REFERENCE           18KYK029
LANG_ENGLISH        "I'm not really sure.  I'll have to catch up with you. Go on ahead without me."
LANG_CZECH        "Nejsem si jisty.  Musime se sejit. Pokracuj beze mne."

